<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>전체 게시글 목록</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #f8f9fa; }
        .board-container { margin-top: 50px; background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .table thead { background-color: #0d6efd; color: white; }
        .content-preview {
            display: inline-block;
            max-width: 300px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container board-container">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
        <h2 class="fw-bold">📋 전체 게시글 목록</h2>
        <a href="/board/create" class="btn btn-primary">글쓰기</a>
    </div>

    <table class="table table-hover text-center">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th style="width: 10%">닉네임</th>
            <th style="width: 40%" class="text-start">제목</th>
            <th style="width: 35%" class="text-start">내용</th>
            <th style="width: 15%">상세보기</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        {{#boards}}
            <tr>
                <td>{{nickname}}</td>
                <td class="text-start fw-bold">{{title}}</td>
                <td class="text-start text-muted">
                    <span class="content-preview">{{content}}</span>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <a href="/board/{{id}}" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">열람</a>
                </td>
            </tr>
        {{/boards}}

        {{^boards}}
            <tr>
                <td colspan="4" class="py-5 text-muted">
                    작성된 게시글이 없습니다. 첫 번째 글을 남겨보세요!
                </td>
            </tr>
        {{/boards}}
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-light border">메인으로</a>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>